-- TCL to Get as Much as $30.9 Million in Subsidies From Shenzhen Government
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-28T23:01:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/tcl-to-get-much-as-30-9-million-in-subsidies-from-shenzhen-government.html

          
          
             TCL Corp. said it will receive as
much as 210 million yuan in subsidies from the government of the
southern Chinese city of Shenzhen, according to a filing to
Shenzhen’s stock exchange.  
 The electronics company’s units have already gotten 341.8
million yuan of subsidies from the Shenzhen government,
according to the statement.  
